                    <span>This wonderful book puts into layperson's terms the scientific lessons of Behavior Analysis.  A must read for anyone who comes into contact with other human beings.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Get the right path in helping yourself!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
